@startuml UC6_ReturnDevice

title UC6 - Return Device (Simple Sequence)

actor User
participant UI
participant System
database Database

User -> UI : Click Return button
UI -> User : Show confirmation popup
User -> UI : Confirm return
UI -> System : Send return request
System -> Database : Update device quantity
Database --> System : Update success
System --> UI : Return success response
UI --> User : Show confirmation

@enduml
